constructPathForTypeList

public static java.lang.String constructPathForTypeList(java.lang.String collectionType,
                                                        java.util.List<java.lang.String> listOfIds)
Constructs the URI path that specifies the target of the push notification. Generally, you should use the other methods in this class to construct the path for you, rather than using this method to do it manually.

Parameters:
collectionType - the collection type to target, usually devices, groups, or users
listOfIds - a List of the UUIDs in that collection to target
